iamond-details/27447053?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&amp;a_cid=55e51e63&amp;chan=blog-informational" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">$83,270</a></strong></td><td><strong>9/10 — Elite 4ct.</strong> VVS2 in a 4-carat stone is very rare. This stone offers incredible internal cleanliness and colorless fire.</td></tr><tr class="highlight-row"><td>4.06ct</td><td>D-VS2 Ideal</td><td><strong><a href="https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/25063251?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&amp;a_cid=55e51e63&amp;chan=blog-informational" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">$85,440</a></strong></td><td><strong>10/10 — The Best 4ct Choice.</strong> D-color is king. At $85k, this stone provides the highest possible color grade at a 4-carat weight.</td></tr><tr><td>5.02ct</td><td>H-VS1 Astor Cut</td><td><strong><a href="https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/25466788?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&amp;a_cid=55e51e63&amp;chan=blog-informational" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">$110,800</a></strong></td><td><strong>9/10 — The Branding Premium.</strong> The "Astor Cut" represents Blue Nile's top 0.1% of cut quality. You are paying for technical perfection in facet alignment.</td></tr><tr class="highlight-row"><td>5.01ct</td><td>D-VS2 Ideal</td><td><strong><a href="https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/19070016?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&amp;a_cid=55e51e63&amp;chan=blog-informational" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">$129,430</a></strong></td><td><strong>10/10 — The Ultimate Crown Jewel.</strong> A 5-carat D-color diamond is the pinnacle of the natural market. This is an investment-grade masterpiece.</td></tr></tbody></table>

